snippet.title: ZikSquare Switch - Trailer (ESRB Everyone)
snippet.description:
Ziksquare is a platformer video game where the music score is the game !

Take on the challenge of the 15 original musics

Create up to 40 personal musics with the
15 instruments and the 4 tracks !

Beat you best scores or the highscores of your friends on your own composition !

Don't want to compose the music but want to create you own levels ?
use the Music Generator included in the game, and replace the generated blocks by the blocks you want to create your gameplay !
(peaks, blocks, electricity, ghost, void, etc.).

Available soon on the Nintendo Switch !
